column3: “Gotta batch the other day and it's almost a 50/50 split. Very mellow and chill stone and gives a little sativa mind rush while the indica relaxes all muscles. Great strain for doing housework on a day off. Nice, sweet smoke reminiscent of sugary strawberries.”
“Had this around a year ago at Breakwater ATC in NJ. It was a special edition strain they only had for awhile. It was a nice flavored Kush with an indica high”
